Karous
WoD 20th Annversary Edition Sheet system
Revision 0.2

Character should be stored in a CouchDB database.  Each character sheet stored
as a document in that database:

Concept sketch:

{
	"objid": "#12345:1614982300",
	"template": [
		"Base",
		"Mage",
		"Technocracy",
		"Void Engineers"
	],
	"faction": [
		"Mage",
		"Technocracy",
		"Void Engineers",
		"Neutralization Specialist Corps"
	],
	"sheet": {
		"Name": "Rico Hernandez Vasquez",
		"Concept: "USMC Ghostbuster",
		"Nature": "Crusader",
		"Demeanor": "Traditionalist"
		"Dexterity": 3,
		"Stamina": 3,
		"Strength": 2,
		"Appearance": 2,
		"Charisma": 2,
		"Manipulation": 2,
		"Intelligence": 4,
		"Perception": 3,
		"Wits": 3,
		"Alertness": 2,
		"Firearms": 2,
		"Science": 2,
		"Energy Weapons": 2,
		"Subdimensions": 2,
